LOC_Yalgrin_WineBridge_Settings_AdvancedProcessIntegration_ToolTip =
    This changes the way certain Linux processes are launched.
        From the technical standpoint it allows you to launch Linux processes as if they were Windows processes.
        It allows for a better integration with certain plugins and is required for some integrations such as Itch.io native client integration.

        Be warned, it can be a bit unstable!
